source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements - Ecological Integrity: Conservation Element Summary (4KM)
source.description: This map presents summaries of conservation elements by reporting unit (4KM) alongside terrestrial intactness and long-term potential for change.  This includes additional dataset focused on non-designated/non-urban lands, and non-designated/non-urban areas on BLM lands.
